| Taxes Payable          | 0.00          | 2023-12-31   | 1143833.89 | 2024-02-05 |
| Total Current Liabilities | 0.00       | 2023-12-31   | 3143833.89 | 2024-02-05 |

No other liability line items are listed.

Step 3: Extract the Relevant Values  
- The initial value of total current liabilities is "0.00".
- The end value of total current liabilities is "3143833.89".

Step 4: Format the Answer According to Instructions
